display_long_description:
This experience is an early demo version of a first-person VR dungeon exploration game.

Players explore a mysterious and atmospheric dungeon where the focus is on observation, anomaly detection, and solving small environmental puzzles. Gameplay is intentionally minimal, emphasizing tension, atmosphere, and careful exploration rather than fast-paced action.

The current build represents an early stage of development. Features, content, and mechanics are subject to change as development continues. Player feedback is highly appreciated and will help shape future updates and improvements.

This demo is designed to showcase the core concept and mood of the experience while laying the foundation for future expansions.
